Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.40,0:00:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉近最喜欢与最讨厌的距离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.20,0:00:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二人的推理与悬疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.80,0:00:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Broadway灿烂的舞台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.80,0:00:06.40,*De,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Broadway:百老汇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.50,0:00:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与兰和妈妈一起遭遇大案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.90,0:00:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看清真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.50,0:00:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 头脑却是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.30,0:00:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.60,0:01:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,横滨中华街的案件解决后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.50,0:01:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰突然晕倒了 在朦胧的意识中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.50,0:01:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起了过去的一件案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.00,0:01:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.90,0:01:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我妈妈带着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.70,0:01:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去纽约看歌舞剧时的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.40,0:02:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剧场门口和妈妈的好友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.20,0:02:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shalon·Vineyard碰头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.20,0:02:05.70,*De,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shalon·Vineyard:莎隆·温雅德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.10,0:02:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由她带领
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.80,0:02:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去参观开演前的舞台布景时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.40,0:02:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天顶上的那个是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.80,0:02:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞台服装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.30,0:02:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没地方放 就挂在顶上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.60,0:02:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.50,0:02:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铠甲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.90,0:02:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.30,0:02:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.10,0:02:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.60,0:03:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工藤新一NY事件（推理篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.40,0:03:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚持一下 兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.30,0:03:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再过一会儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.00,0:03:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再过一会儿就到医院了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.90,0:03:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.30,0:03:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.30,0:03:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.30,0:03:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.50,0:03:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是冲着我来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.50,0:03:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁要杀我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.40,0:03:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.30,0:03:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绳子旧了 断了而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.00,0:03:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 是谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.50,0:03:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个铠甲也挂上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.90,0:03:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 不幸中的大幸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.30,0:03:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁边的那个大镜子没有碎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.70,0:04:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是我们的守护神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.40,0:04:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.10,0:04:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要感谢的不是镜子 也不是上帝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.10,0:04:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是这个孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.80,0:04:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你救了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.70,0:04:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.60,0:04:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该准备准备了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.80,0:04:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 结束之后再来后台吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.70,0:04:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.00,0:04:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出血了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.00,0:04:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创可贴 创可贴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.80,0:04:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.90,0:04:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上帝到底还是没有的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.20,0:04:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有的话 也不会发生这起惨剧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.30,0:04:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 有希子 我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shalon你不看完再走吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.60,0:04:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是想看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.00,0:04:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却突然有件推不掉的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.50,0:04:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚好像会有狂风暴雨 所以就不看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.80,0:05:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.10,0:05:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.60,0:05:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么豪华的舞会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.30,0:05:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在日本是看不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.20,0:05:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不这么想的小鬼也有一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.20,0:05:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易来的 认真点看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.20,0:05:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有什么好看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.50,0:05:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是根据古希腊神话编的爱情故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.20,0:05:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 希腊神话原作是怎么讲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.40,0:05:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金苹果啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.50,0:05:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.50,0:05:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hera, Athene和Aphrodite三位女神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.50,0:05:57.40,*De,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hera:赫拉 Athene:雅典娜 Aphrodite:阿佛洛狄忒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.30,0:06:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然一天被叫去庆祝宴会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.90,0:06:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而没有被叫去产生嫉妒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.20,0:06:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eris女神把一个金苹果送给她们三个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.20,0:06:08.30,*De,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eris:伊里斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.80,0:06:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面写着──给最美丽的女神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.50,0:06:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不就是刚才的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.10,0:06:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个 然后这三个女神为了决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.70,0:06:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁最应该得到这个金苹果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.60,0:06:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后决定由特洛伊王子来选择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.60,0:06:24.20,*De,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特洛伊(Tory)王子:帕里斯(Paris)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.60,0:06:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们都对王子许诺若选自己就予以重酬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.70,0:06:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 那个演没落贵族的刚才的那个大演员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.30,0:06:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是特洛伊王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.50,0:06:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演有钱人的妻子的女演员是主神Zeus的妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.50,0:06:41.20,*De,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zeus:宙斯,天神之父,地上万物的最高统治者,诸神之神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.50,0:06:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许诺给他地上最大的权力的婚姻女神Hera
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.50,0:06:46.00,*De,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hera:赫拉,宙斯的姊姊与妻子,女性的代表,掌管婚姻和生育,善妒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.40,0:06:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着挺厉害的那个日裔女演员演的就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.30,0:06:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许诺使他战争胜利的智慧女神Athene
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.30,0:06:54.40,*De,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Athene:雅典娜,智慧女神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.20,0:06:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个非常性感的女演员演的就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.40,0:07:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许诺给他绝世美色的美神Aphrodite
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.40,0:07:02.10,*De,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aphrodite:阿佛洛狄忒,爱与美之神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.00,0:07:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而前面的那个场面里暗自看着三人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.20,0:07:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个阴险的女演员演的就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.10,0:07:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送金苹果的不和女神Eris
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.40,0:07:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个戏里把权力改成金钱 战争改成工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.70,0:07:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝世美女改成浪漫爱情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.80,0:07:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金苹果改成苹果形状镶着很多宝石的豪华项链
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.80,0:07:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来呢 谁选中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.50,0:07:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aphrodite
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.30,0:07:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 就是因为这个爆发了特洛伊战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.80,0:07:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这是希腊神话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.30,0:07:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个歌舞剧可不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.60,0:07:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果看到那个没落贵族的真面目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.30,0:07:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会大吃一惊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.20,0:07:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 可怜的人类们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.50,0:07:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是Michael
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.50,0:07:59.10,*De,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michael:米迦勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.70,0:08:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michael 那个大天使吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.60,0:08:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太假了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.40,0:08:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我的回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.50,0:08:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.10,0:09:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heath
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.10,0:09:04.80,*De,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heath:西斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.70,0:09:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.30,0:09:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 一定是恶作剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.30,0:09:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不是恶作剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.10,0:09:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.30,0:09:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.30,0:09:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被枪打了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.90,0:09:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.80,0:09:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也先避一避吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.30,0:09:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 兰拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.50,0:09:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.70,0:09:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.50,0:09:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.20,0:09:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子弹壳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.60,0:09:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.60,0:09:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.30,0:10:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被杀的竟然是Heath
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.30,0:10:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们认识吗 警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.40,0:10:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的妻子是他的狂热戏迷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.70,0:10:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的情况怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.50,0:10:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演员都让他们在后台等着呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.30,0:10:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人都逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.80,0:10:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子弹穿过胸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.80,0:10:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嵌在后背的翅膀上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.80,0:10:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.00,0:10:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.30,0:10:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据子弹的射入角度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.00,0:10:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被上方40度的角度来的子弹击中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.00,0:10:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,40度 非常高啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.50,0:10:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.00,0:10:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是从那边的包厢打的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.40,0:10:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用激光瞄准器瞄准的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.60,0:10:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Night baroness
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.60,0:10:48.70,*De,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Night baroness:暗夜男爵夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.40,0:10:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是有希子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.40,0:10:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.80,0:10:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也来看戏呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.00,0:11:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌舞剧变成悬念剧真是没有想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.00,0:11:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被击中的时候是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.10,0:11:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高潮天使登场的场面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.90,0:11:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化学药剂做的烟雾弥漫开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.00,0:11:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着镜子里映出来的天使的映像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.40,0:11:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向上方滑行的同时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.80,0:11:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装扮成天使的Heath
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.50,0:11:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从镜子后面升上来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.70,0:11:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来就像是从镜子里出来了一样的幻像场面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.10,0:11:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.00,0:11:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是在他从镜子后出来的瞬间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.70,0:11:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从包厢开枪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.10,0:11:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.30,0:11:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.20,0:11:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往舞台上扔手枪应该是为了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.20,0:11:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让剧场混乱他好逃跑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.20,0:11:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 是真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.00,0:11:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从包厢瞄的准
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.40,0:11:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.50,0:11:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衬着舞台上喷出的烟雾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.00,0:11:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那个包厢到舞台间的红色激光能清楚地看见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.00,0:11:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我儿子也看见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.50,0:11:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.50,0:12:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就在你旁边吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.70,0:12:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回是真人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.20,0:12:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个少年就是你引以为傲的儿子新一吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.30,0:12:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 和优作长得很像吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.30,0:12:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也喜欢恶作剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.00,0:12:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.70,0:12:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.40,0:12:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.90,0:12:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.50,0:12:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你安分点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.00,0:12:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.30,0:12:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有希子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.70,0:12:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如你所言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.30,0:12:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个月前有个可疑的人特意买了那个破位子的票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.30,0:12:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴着围巾和帽子 也不知道是男的还是女的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.10,0:12:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人就是那个人没有错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.50,0:12:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那是个破位子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.80,0:12:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里很高所以应该是好位子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.40,0:12:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个包厢比较偏 看不清舞台 是便宜的位子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.20,0:13:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预定这样的位子 遮着脸去买票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.00,0:13:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容易让人记住 正是犯人想要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.60,0:13:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.30,0:13:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸体上剩下的这两个奇妙的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.90,0:13:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇妙的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.00,0:13:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 脖子上有个烫伤的痕迹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.40,0:13:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有右手上沾着的血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.40,0:13:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右手是不是因为他摸了自己的胸口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.70,0:13:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 问题是手心里的血迹被蹭过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.90,0:13:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手上沾了血之后摸过什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.70,0:13:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的衣服上也没有血迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.30,0:13:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被击中之后就什么也摸不了了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.80,0:13:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个谜你这个Night baroness也解不开吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.70,0:13:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.50,0:13:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么去问问优作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.40,0:13:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是他的话一定知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.00,0:13:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.60,0:14:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在优作正在洛杉矶的旅馆里憋着写作呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.80,0:14:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可难办了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.20,0:14:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么有名的人被杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.20,0:14:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是让犯人逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.10,0:14:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还没有找到任何线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.80,0:14:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公众 署长和我太太会对我说什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.40,0:14:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样的话 让新一来解决不行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.30,0:14:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让新一来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.70,0:14:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.90,0:14:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子还是个小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.70,0:14:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现实中发生的杀人案怎么能行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.10,0:14:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是新一解决了飞机里发生的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.60,0:14:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是在犯人抓住之后给兰悄悄地解说的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.90,0:14:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如我所想之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.10,0:14:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此这般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.50,0:14:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 一开始就很利索地参加了搜查的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.10,0:14:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.60,0:14:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.50,0:14:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后把怀疑对象召集起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.70,0:14:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很了不起地说出了真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.40,0:14:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像Holmes和Poirot似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.40,0:14:59.60,*De,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes:福尔摩斯 Poirot:波洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.40,0:15:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个新一啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.30,0:15:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人就在那四个女演员里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.30,0:15:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.90,0:15:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案件发生之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.10,0:15:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去那个包厢看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.10,0:15:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉落在那里的子弹壳根本不热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.60,0:15:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就说明是谁预先放在那里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.90,0:15:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 新一也看见了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.10,0:15:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激光瞄准器的红色激光是从那个包厢射出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.60,0:15:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.30,0:15:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们实际上看不出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.20,0:15:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个红色的激光是从哪边射向哪边的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.60,0:15:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 估计那个激光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.80,0:15:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是从包厢 而是从舞台上发射的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.20,0:15:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了让我们认为有人从上面瞄准
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.20,0:15:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.30,0:16:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遮着脸去买那个位子的票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.90,0:16:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送来奇怪的包裹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.00,0:16:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是为了让人认为有可疑的人盯上了自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.60,0:16:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而做的陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.20,0:16:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.20,0:16:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.50,0:16:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 这也是其中一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.50,0:16:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不就是开演前铠甲掉下来的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.60,0:16:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看这个地板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.90,0:16:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被钉子钩住的细铁丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.60,0:16:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一端是刀之类切过的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.20,0:16:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且掉下来的铠甲上也有细铁丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.40,0:16:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是谁故意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.20,0:16:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是用鞋子上带的刀把细铁丝切断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.30,0:16:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让铠甲掉下来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.50,0:16:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要带作为Shalon朋友的我们参观后台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.50,0:16:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以知道我们是会走过这里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.40,0:17:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 当时只要是在场的人 都可能放下铠甲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.70,0:17:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射杀Heath时 和他一起上台的演员就
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.50,0:17:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既可以伪装客席上的激光瞄准人 也可以枪杀他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.60,0:17:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那四个女神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.90,0:17:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.90,0:17:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 他的身高是6尺3寸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.80,0:17:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们都在6尺以下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.70,0:17:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比自己高 而且还藏在镜子后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.80,0:17:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能够从上方射杀呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.00,0:17:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 是怎么干的呢 新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.20,0:17:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有考虑到那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.70,0:17:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.40,0:17:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的话是真的吗 Lira
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.40,0:17:55.50,*De,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lira:里拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.80,0:17:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 Heath和我相爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.50,0:18:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经五年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.60,0:18:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你知道他和我在谈恋爱还
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.40,0:18:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吵了 你们两个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.70,0:18:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候还说这些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.10,0:18:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最不安的是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.40,0:18:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的男友却另外有两个女友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.90,0:18:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 难道Rose
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.90,0:18:24.50,*De,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rose:罗斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.80,0:18:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.90,0:18:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.40,0:18:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样的话她们四个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.50,0:18:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,围绕着Heath还真的没准有点什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.30,0:18:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.40,0:18:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和三个人相好我能理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.00,0:18:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个Iberis不是和他没有什么关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.00,0:18:40.80,*De,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Iberis:伊贝丽丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.80,0:18:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同于其他三人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.20,0:18:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的镜子上没有贴他的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.20,0:18:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 Heath和Iberis是夫妇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.60,0:18:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参观后台时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.50,0:18:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shalon悄悄告诉我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.50,0:19:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为怕不受欢迎 所以剧团里的人也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.30,0:19:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此她恨他和那三个人相好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.30,0:19:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.30,0:19:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是怎么从上面射杀他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.80,0:19:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.70,0:19:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离镜子最近的是Rose
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.20,0:19:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演的是被天使惊吓 晕倒的情节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.30,0:19:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Iberis弯着腰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.00,0:19:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜跪下祈祷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.40,0:19:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位置最高的是站着抱头的Lira
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.90,0:19:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他三人被烟雾遮住了下半身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.30,0:19:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的手却是可以看清楚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.20,0:19:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是拿着手枪的话 立刻就会被发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.10,0:19:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是Heath蹲下了
